{"tid":1057730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合航空波音737-900型客機引擎故障急降　乘客：引擎冒出火光 (08:21) 2019/3/12","createTime":"2019-03-12T05:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T11:03:14.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea101f42473931f3d73cfe1468f0039e9326b93","tid":1057730,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190312/s00005/583eaf37a8dcf336c4952aa983c08a0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190312%2Fs00005%2F583eaf37a8dcf336c4952aa983c08a0f.jpg&h=cad08243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國聯合航空表示，一架載有180人的波音737-900型客機，飛行途中引擎故障停止運作，急降得州喬治布殊州際機場。機上乘客全部安全，部分人用充氣滑梯逃生時受輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n涉事客機於新澤西州紐瓦克機場起飛，當時載有174名乘客及6名機組人員。客機於當地時間周日（10日）晚飛至得州喬治布殊州際機場附近時引擎故障，被迫緊急降落。<br />\n<br />\n有機上乘客表示，當時聽到一聲巨響後，飛機突然猛烈搖晃，並看見機艙外有一道閃光；有乘客稱，看到飛機引擎冒出火光。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦航空管理局表示，飛機着陸後，應急部門並未發現客機有火光或冒煙，當局正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n（彭博新聞）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190312/s00005/1552349280638/聯合航空波音737-900型客機引擎故障急降-乘客-引擎冒出火光\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190312%2Fs00005%2F1552349280638%2F%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%B3%A2%E9%9F%B3737-900%E5%9E%8B%E5%AE%A2%E6%A9%9F%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%80%A5%E9%99%8D-%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2-%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E%E5%86%92%E5%87%BA%E7%81%AB%E5%85%89&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6AOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=f054e7ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190312%2Fs00005%2F1552349280638%2F%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%B3%A2%E9%9F%B3737-900%E5%9E%8B%E5%AE%A2%E6%A9%9F%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%80%A5%E9%99%8D-%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2-%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E%E5%86%92%E5%87%BA%E7%81%AB%E5%85%89&h=a2d195a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190312/s00005/1552349280638/聯合航空波音737-900型客機引擎故障急降-乘客-引擎冒出火光</a>"},{"pid":"ded7377b16df05a1de7b33ad5c5dd47ed26d09e3","tid":1057730,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:43:19.000Z","msg":"個別事件啫"},{"pid":"614fc1b6dac287e6fbe75bdc34eecc9e5230c0a6","tid":1057730,"uid":56954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:50:13.000Z","msg":"single or both?"},{"pid":"7cd5734c4a0536dc114355749594ffadf776a252","tid":1057730,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T09:24:22.000Z","msg":"又是737"},{"pid":"8f21ec6be71bab485884f024041b5446fc553c69","tid":1057730,"uid":162272,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"今次只係引擎故障停止運作，無造成任何人受傷。況且係上一代機型，唔好放大件事。"},{"pid":"a9fb0278bbfdbcbaf34fa112e4969bbe7097e9ae","tid":1057730,"uid":85071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:03:14.000Z","msg":"得你老母州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n德州啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}